302
00:17:35,415 --> 00:17:39,319
people with PTSD for various reasons have mentioned, especially veterans with PTSD,

303
00:17:40,079 --> 00:17:46,685
things like it's important to have audio tracks that will be specifically for things that

304
00:17:46,705 --> 00:17:52,109
could be contentious. For example, a gunfire could be an issue. A medic, someone shouting

305
00:17:52,149 --> 00:17:56,053
out for a medic or yelling and bleeding out can be an issue. Now, the actual concept of

306
00:17:56,553 --> 00:18:00,756
Gun warfare may not be the problem in itself, it could just be very specific things like that.

