00:26:30,357 --> 00:26:31,858
and executive producer and work your way up

446
00:26:31,898 --> 00:26:33,159
depending on how big your company is.

447
00:26:34,620 --> 00:26:37,221
But yeah, it's challenging.

448
00:26:37,441 --> 00:26:40,803
Like, and be aware that small steps matter.

